-- TNK-BP Board to Discuss Airport Fueling Purchase Feb. 27
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-02-20T15:38:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/tnk-bp-board-to-discuss-airport-fueling-purchase-feb-27.html
TNK-BP, BP Plc.’s Russian venture
with a group of billionaires, said it’s studying buying the
fueling complex for Koltsovo airport in Ekaterinburg.  The board of the Moscow-based company will examine the
possible purchase at a Feb. 27 meeting, it said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
